Third Department,

October, 1939.

(October 4, 1939.) The People of the State of New York ex rel. Edward Henry Gibson, alias Jack H. Smith, v. William E. Snyder, as Warden of Clinton Prison, Dannemora, N. Y.

Motion for permission to present record and brief in handwriting denied. Present — Hill, P. J., Crapser, Bliss, Hefíernan and Sehenek, JJ.
